{
    "title": "Camarão que dorme a onda Leva",
    "artist": "Zeca Pagodinho",
    "composer": "Zeca Pagodinho / Arlindo Cruz / Jorge Aragão / Beto Sem Braço",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não pense que meu coração é de papel</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não brinque com o meu interior</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Camarão que dorme a onda leva</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Hoje é o dia da caça, amanhã do caçador</span>\n\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não quero que nosso amor acabe assim</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um coração quando ama é sempre amigo</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Só não faça gato e sapato de mi__im</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F5+\">F5+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pois aquele que dá pão, também dá castigo</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não pense que meu coração</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não pense que meu coração é de papel</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não brinque com o meu interior</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Camarão que dorme a onda leva</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Hoje é dia da caça, amanhã do caçador</span>\n\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não veja meu sentimento com desde__ém</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Enquanto o bem existir o mal tem cura</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A pedra é muito forte mas tem um porém, meu bem</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb6\">Eb6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A água tanto bate até que fura</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não pense que meu coração</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não pense que meu coração é de papel</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não brinque com o meu interior</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Camarão que dorme a onda leva</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Hoje é dia da caça, amanhã do caçador</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Hoje é dia da caça, amanhã do caçador</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F/A\">F/A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não pense que meu coração</span>\n",
